encies\n424: \n425: ```\n426: Phase 1 (Control Plane) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n427: T1.1-T1.3 (Init/Auth/URL tests) ──┬── T1.4-T1.5 (Session tests)\n428:                                   └── T1.6 (Close test)\n429: \n430: Phase 2 (Data Plane) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n431: T2.1-T2.3 (Init/Header/URL tests) ──┬── T2.4-T2.5 (Execute/Write tests)\n432:                                      ├── T2.6-T2.7 (Upload/Download tests)\n433:                                      ├── T2.8 (ListFiles test)\n434:                                      └── T2.9 (Close test)\n435: \n436: Phase 3 (Code Interpreter) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n437: T3.1-T3.2 (Init/Session tests) ──┬── T3.3-T3.4 (Context/Stop tests)\n438:                                   ├── T3.5-T3.6 (Execute/RunCode tests)\n439:                                   ├── T3.7-T3.8 (FileOps/Verbose tests)\n440:                                   └── T3.9 (Failure test)\n441: \n442: Phase 4 (Agent Runtime Client) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n443: T4.1-T4.3 (Init/URL tests) ──┬── T4.4-T4.5 (Session tests)\n444:                               ├── T4.6 (DataPlane init)\n445:                               ├── T4.7 (ContextManager)\n446:                               ├── T4.8 (Invoke)\n447:                               └── T4.9 (Close)\n448: \n449: Phase 5 (Agent Runtime Data Plane) ────────────────────────────────────────────\n450: T5.1-T5.4 (Init/Header/URL/Pool tests) ──┬── T5.5 (Bootstrap)\n451:                                           ├── T5.6-T5.7 (Invoke/Headers)\n452:                                           ├── T5.8 (Timeout)\n453:                                           └── T5.9 (Close)\n454: \n455: Phase 6 (Integration) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n456: T6.1-T6.3 (Lifecycle/Workflow/Reuse tests) ──┬── T6.4 (Bootstrap failure)\n457:                                               