st_exceptions.py` | Verify | 66 | Exception tests (4 classes) |\n535: | `sdk-python/tests/test_utils.py` | Verify | 71 | Utility tests (3 classes) |\n536: | `sdk-python/tests/test_exports.py` | Verify | 38 | Export tests (2 classes) |\n537: \n538: **Total: 9 test files, ~1,428 test lines, 47 test classes**\n539: \n540: ---\n541: \n542: ## Implementation Notes\n543: \n544: ### Test Execution Requirements\n545: \n546: ```bash\n547: # Install test dependencies\n548: pip install pytest pytest-mock pytest-cov responses pytest-benchmark pytest-xdist\n549: \n550: # Run all tests\n551: pytest sdk-python/tests/ -v\n552: \n553: # Run with coverage\n554: pytest sdk-python/tests/ --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing\n555: \n556: # Run in parallel\n557: pytest sdk-python/tests/ -n auto\n558: ```\n559: \n560: ### Coverage Targets\n561: \n562: | Module | Target Coverage | Current Tests |\n563: |--------|-----------------|---------------|\n564: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | 100% | `test_exports.py` |\n565: | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | 95%+ | `test_code_interpreter.py` |\n566: | `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | 95%+ | `test_agent_runtime_client.py` |\n567: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | 95%+ | `test_control_plane.py` |\n568: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | 95%+ | `test_data_plane.py` |\n569: | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | 95%+ | `test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py` |\n570: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | 100% | `test_exceptions.py` |\n571: | `agentcube/utils/*.py` | 95%+ | `test_utils.py` |\n572: \n573: ### Test Patterns Used\n574: \n575: 1. **Wire-level mocking**: `responses` library for HTTP interception\n576: 2. **Object-level mocking**: `MagicMock` for response objects\n577: 3. **Dependency-level mocking**: `patch` for class replacement\n578: 4. **Parameter validation**: Environment variable cleanup tests\n579: 5. **Delegation testing**: Mock delegation method calls\n580: 6. **Cleanup verification**: Mock cleanup method assertions\n581: 7. **HTTP contract testing**: JSON body format validation\n582: 8. **Integration workflow**: Full lifecycle tests\n583: \n584: ---\n585: \n586: ## Implementation Timeline\n587: \n588: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n589: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n590: | Phase 1: Control Plane | T1.1-T1.6 | Pending | 0% |\n591: | Phase 2: Data Plane | T2.1-T2.9 | Pending | 0% |\n592: | Phase 3: Code Interpreter | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n593: | Phase 4: Agent Runtime Client | T4.1-T4.9 | Pending | 0% |\n594: | Phase 5: Agent Runtime Data Plane | T5.1-T5.9 | Pending | 0% |\n595: | Phase 6: Integration | T6.1-T6.5 | Pending | 0% |\n596: | Phase 7: Exceptions | T7.1-T7.4 | Pending | 0% |\n597: | Phase 8: Utils | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n598: | Phase 9: Exports | T9.1-T9.2 | Pending | 0% |\n599: | Phase 10: Coverage | T10.1-T10.10 | Pending | 0% |\n600: | Phase 11: Enhancements | T11.1-T11.6 | Pending | 0% |\n601: | Phase 12: Full Suite | T12.1-T12.4 | Pending | 0% |\n602: \n603: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/78 tasks)**\n604: \n605: ---\n606: \n607: ## References\n608: \n609: - Design: `sdk-python/tests/design.md`\n610: - Test Files: `sdk-python/tests/*.py`\n611: - AgentCube Package: `sdk-python/agentcube/`\n612: - pytest Documentation: https://docs.pytest.org/\n613: - responses Library: https://github.com/getsentry/responses\n614: - pytest-cov: https://pytest-cov.readthedocs.io/\n\n(End of file - total 614 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试 |\n| Module | sdk-python/tests |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Control Plane Tests Verification (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Verify `TestControlPlaneClientInit` tests pass\n  - Purpose: Validate default/custom timeout and session creation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces