race` flag for thread safety verification\n664: \n665: ### Benchmark Template\n666: \n667: ```go\n668: func BenchmarkOperation(b *testing.B) {\n669:     setup := createTestSetup(b)\n670:     b.ResetTimer()\n671:     for i := 0; i < b.N; i++ {\n672:         _ = setup.performOperation()\n673:     }\n674: }\n675: ```\n676: \n677: ### Mock Store Template\n678: \n679: ```go\n680: type MockStore struct {\n681:     GetFunc    func(ctx context.Context, id string) (*SandboxInfo, error)\n682:     StoreFunc  func(ctx context.Context, sandbox *SandboxInfo) error\n683: }\n684: ```\n685: \n686: ### Coverage Target\n687: \n688: Minimum coverage requirements per package:\n689: - pkg/router: 85%\n690: - pkg/store: 90%\n691: - pkg/picod: 80%\n692: \n693: ---\n694: \n695: ## Implementation Timeline\n696: \n697: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n698: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n699: | Phase 1: Router JWT | T1.1-T1.6 | Pending | 0% |\n700: | Phase 2: Router Server | T2.1-T2.6 | Pending | 0% |\n701: | Phase 3: Router Session Manager | T3.1-T3.6 | Pending | 0% |\n702: | Phase 4: Router Middleware | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n703: | Phase 5: Router Auth Middleware | T5.1-T5.6 | Pending | 0% |\n704: | Phase 6: Router Errors | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n705: | Phase 7: Router Reverse Proxy | T7.1-T7.5 | Pending | 0% |\n706: | Phase 8: Router Config | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n707: | Phase 9: Store Redis | T9.1-T9.6 | Pending | 0% |\n708: | Phase 10: Store Valkey | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n709: | Phase 11: Store Interface | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n710: | Phase 12: Picod Auth | T12.1-T12.5 | Pending | 0% |\n711: | Phase 13: Picod Execute | T13.1-T13.5 | Pending | 0% |\n712: | Phase 14: Picod Files | T14.1-T14.5 | Pending | 0% |\n713: | Phase 15: Picod Sanitize | T15.1-T15.4 | Pending | 0% |\n714: | Phase 16: Picod Server | T16.1-T16.5 | Pending | 0% |\n715: | Phase 17: Coverage Verification | T17.1-T17.5 | Pending | 0% |\n716: | Phase 18: Race Detector | T18.1-T18.4 | Pending | 0% |\n717: \n718: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/86 tasks)**\n719: \n720: ---\n721: \n722: ## References\n723: \n724: - Design: `changes/AR-039/design.md`\n725: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md`\n726: - Proposal: `changes/AR-039/proposal.md`\n727: - Spec: `changes/AR-039/spec.md`\n728: - Root Delta Spec: `delta-spec.md`\n729: - pkg/router directory: `pkg/router/`\n730: - pkg/store directory: `pkg/store/`\n731: - pkg/picod directory: `pkg/picod/`\n732: - Go Testing Guide: https://golang.org/doc/tutorial/addatest\n733: - Testify Documentation: https://github.com/stretchr/testify\n734: - Go Race Detector: https://golang.org/doc/articles/race_detector.html\n\n(End of file - total 734 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) |\n| Module | pkg |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Router JWT Tests Enhancement (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Add test for `NewJWTManagerWithClient` with valid k8s client\n  - Purpose: Test JWT manager creation with Kubernetes client","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-039/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775902159132,"end":1775902159169}}}}
