{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775902452156,"sessionID":"ses_283fc6b03ffekIl93FHMkYZPci","part":{"id":"prt_d7c08e929001MyJxoCCL76IHox","messageID":"msg_d7c04718f001Eyvv6X016LNauO","sessionID":"ses_283fc6b03ffekIl93FHMkYZPci","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8d4b06bacebf40be98697f916ea6db53","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-041/tasks.md","content":"# AR-041 — E2E 集成测试 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-041 — E2E 集成测试 |\n| Module | test/e2e |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: E2E Framework Setup (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `test/e2e/framework/` directory structure\n  - Purpose: Establish E2E test framework foundation\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/`\n  - Verification: `ls -la test/e2e/framework/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Implement `framework/test_context.go` with TestContext struct\n  - Purpose: Define test context with K8s client, HTTP client, cleanup hooks\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/test_context.go`\n  - Verification: `go build test/e2e/framework/test_context.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Implement `framework/kube_client.go` with Kubernetes client helpers\n  - Purpose: Provide K8s client initialization utilities\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/kube_client.go`\n  - Verification: `go build test/e2e/framework/kube_client.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Implement `framework/http_client.go` with HTTP test clients\n  - Purpose: Create SandboxTestClient, RouterTestClient, PicoDTestClient\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/http_client.go`\n  - Verification: `go build test/e2e/framework/http_client.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.5**: Implement `framework/wait_helpers.go` with wait utilities\n  - Purpose: Provide WaitForPodRunning, WaitForPodDeleted, WaitForSandboxReady\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/wait_helpers.go`\n  - Verification: `go build test/e2e/framework/wait_helpers.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.6**: Implement `framework/fixture_manager.go` for fixture loading\n  - Purpose: Load YAML fixtures and manage cleanup\n  - File: `test/e2e/framework/fixture_manager.go`\n  - Verification: `go build test/e2e/framework/fixture_manager.go`\n\n### Phase 2: Test Fixtures Creation (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create `test/e2e/fixtures/` directory\n  - Purpose: Establish test fixtures repository\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/`\n  - Verification: `ls -la test/e2e/fixtures/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Implement `fixtures/echo_agent.yaml` AgentRuntime fixture\n  - Purpose: Provide echo agent for Router invocation tests\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/echo_agent.yaml`\n  - Verification: `kubectl apply -f test/e2e/fixtures/echo_agent.yaml --dry-run=client`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Implement `fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` CodeInterpreter fixture\n  - Purpose: Provide code interpreter for PicoD execution tests\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml`\n  - Verification: `kubectl apply -f test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml --dry-run=client`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Implement `fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` WarmPool fixture\n  - Purpose: Provide warm pool configuration for allocation tests\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml`\n  - Verification: `kubectl apply -f test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml --dry-run=client`\n\n- [ ] **T2.5**: Create `fixtures/test_data/` directory\n  - Purpose: Store test scripts and data files\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/`\n  - Verification: `ls -la test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.6**: Implement `fixtures/test_data/simple_script.py` test script\n  - Purpose: Provide Python script for successful execution tests\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/simple_script.py`\n  - Verification: `python3 test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/simple_script.py`\n\n- [ ] **T2.7**: Implement `fixtures/test_data/error_script.py` error script\n  - Purpose: Provide Python script with syntax error for error handling tests\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/error_script.py`\n  - Verification: `python3 test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/error_script.py 2>&1 | grep SyntaxError`\n\n- [ ] **T2.8**: Implement `fixtures/test_data/large_file.txt` large file fixture\n  - Purpose: Provide large file for upload/download tests (1MB+)\n  - File: `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/large_file.txt`\n  - Verification: `ls -lh test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/large_file.txt | grep -E \"[1-9][0-9]*K|M\"`\n\n### Phase 3: E2E Test Suite Entry Point (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Implement `test/e2e/e2e_test.go` TestMain entry point\n  - Purpose: Initialize test suite with flags and environment setup\n  - File: `test/e2e/e2e_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestMain ./test/e2e/ -count=1`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Add test flags for workload-manager-url, router-url, api-token, namespace\n  - Purpose: Configure E2E test environment via flags\n  - File: `test/e2e/e2e_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v ./test/e2e/ -workload-manager-url=http://localhost:8080 -router-url=http://localhost:8081 -api-token=test -namespace=test`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Implement test suite registration with cleanup hooks\n  - Purpose: Ensure all tests cleanup resources on completion\n  - File: `test/e2e/e2e_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v ./test/e2e/ -run TestE2ESuite`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Add Skip condition for short test mode\n  - Purpose: Allow skipping E2E tests with `-short` flag\n  - File: `test/e2e/e2e_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -short ./test/e2e/ | grep \"skipping\"`\n\n### Phase 4: WorkloadManager E2E Tests (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Implement `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go` TestSandboxCreate\n  - Purpose: Verify POST /v1/sandbox creates sandbox pod\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestSandboxCreate ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Implement TestSandboxGet for GET /v1/sandbox/:namespace/:name\n  - Purpose: Verify sandbox info retrieval\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestSandboxGet ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Implement TestSandboxDelete for DELETE /v1/sandbox/:namespace/:name\n  - Purpose: Verify sandbox cleanup\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestSandboxDelete ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4**: Implement TestSandboxIdempotency for repeated creation\n  - Purpose: Verify same sessionId returned for same name\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestSandboxIdempotency ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5**: Implement TestSandboxInvalidInput for validation errors\n  - Purpose: Verify 400 response for invalid requests\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestSandboxInvalidInput ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.6**: Implement TestHealthEndpoints for /health/live and /health/ready\n  - Purpose: Verify WorkloadManager health probes\n  - File: `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestHealthEndpoints ./test/e2e/`\n\n### Phase 5: Router E2E Tests (ST-5)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1**: Implement `test/e2e/router_test.go` TestRouterAuthIntercept\n  - Purpose: Verify 401 for missing/invalid token, 200 for valid token\n  - File: `test/e2e/router_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestRouterAuthIntercept ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2**: Implement TestRouterSessionRouting for AgentRuntime invocation\n  - Purpose: Verify POST proxied to sandbox pod\n  - File: `test/e2e/router_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestRouterSessionRouting ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3**: Implement TestRouterCodeInterpreterInvocation for CI proxy\n  - Purpose: Verify CodeInterpreter invocation with session header\n  - File: `test/e2e/router_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestRouterCodeInterpreterInvocation ./test/e2e/`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4**: Implement TestRouterSessionHeaderPropagation\n  - Purpose: Verify x-agentcube-session-id header