 ] WorkloadManager E2E tests pass (6 tests: create, get, delete, idempotency, validation, health)\n- [ ] Router E2E tests pass (6 tests: auth, routing, invocation, headers, JWT, health)\n- [ ] PicoD E2E tests pass (6 tests: execute, error, upload, list, download, auth)\n- [ ] Session Store E2E tests pass (4 tests: set/get, TTL, cleanup, concurrent)\n- [ ] Idle Cleanup E2E tests pass (3 tests: cleanup, leader election, resource deletion)\n- [ ] Warm Pool E2E tests pass (3 tests: creation, allocation, replenishment)\n- [ ] CRD Lifecycle E2E tests pass (4 tests: AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, status, deletion)\n- [ ] client-go E2E tests pass (4 tests: typed client, informer, lister, namespace)\n- [ ] Python SDK E2E test directory created with pytest configuration\n- [ ] Python CodeInterpreter E2E tests pass (6 tests: context, execute, files, run_code, exceptions)\n- [ ] Python AgentRuntime E2E tests pass (5 tests: context, invoke, session reuse, exceptions)\n- [ ] run_e2e.sh enhanced with parallel, grouping, logs, timeout, diagnostics\n- [ ] Kind configuration enhanced with Redis, multi-node, port mappings\n- [ ] Makefile E2E targets added (e2e, e2e-parallel, component-specific)\n- [ ] Go module dependencies added (e2e-framework, kind, helm, docker, redis)\n- [ ] Python SDK pytest configuration updated for E2E marker\n- [ ] Integration E2E tests pass (4 tests: full workflow, multi-sandbox, cross-component, SDK+Go)\n- [ ] Full E2E test suite runs successfully with resource cleanup\n- [ ] E2E test execution report generated\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines | Description |\n|------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| `test/e2e/framework/test_context.go` | Create | ~80 | TestContext struct with cleanup hooks |\n| `test/e2e/framework/kube_client.go` | Create | ~60 | Kubernetes client helpers |\n| `test/e2e/framework/http_client.go` | Create | ~180 | SandboxTestClient, RouterTestClient, PicoDTestClient |\n| `test/e2e/framework/wait_helpers.go` | Create | ~50 | WaitForPodRunning, WaitForPodDeleted |\n| `test/e2e/framework/fixture_manager.go` | Create | ~40 | Fixture loading and cleanup |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/echo_agent.yaml` | Create | ~30 | Echo AgentRuntime fixture |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` | Create | ~40 | CodeInterpreter fixture |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` | Create | ~50 | WarmPool fixture |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/simple_script.py` | Create | ~5 | Simple Python test script |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/error_script.py` | Create | ~3 | Error Python script |\n| `test/e2e/fixtures/test_data/large_file.txt` | Create | ~1MB | Large test file |\n| `test/e2e/e2e_test.go` | Create | ~40 | TestMain entry point with flags |\n| `test/e2e/sandbox_test.go` | Create | ~150 | WorkloadManager E2E tests (6 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/router_test.go` | Create | ~180 | Router E2E tests (6 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/code_execution_test.go` | Create | ~150 | PicoD E2E tests (6 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/session_test.go` | Create | ~100 | Session Store E2E tests (4 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/idle_cleanup_test.go` | Create | ~80 | Idle Cleanup E2E tests (3 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/warm_pool_test.go` | Create | ~80 | Warm Pool E2E tests (3 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/crd_lifecycle_test.go` | Create | ~120 | CRD Lifecycle E2E tests (4 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/clientgo_test.go` | Create | ~100 | client-go E2E tests (4 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/python_tests/conftest.py` | Create | ~50 | pytest E2E configuration |\n| `test/e2e/python_tests/__init__.py` | Create | ~1 | Package marker |\n| `test/e2e/python_tests/test_e2e_code_interpreter.py` | Create | ~180 | Python SDK CodeInterpreter E2E tests |\n| `test/e2e/python_tests/test_e2e_agent_runtime.py` | Create | ~150 | Python SDK AgentRuntime E2E tests |\n| `test/e2e/integration_test.go` | Create | ~120 | Integration E2E tests (4 tests) |\n| `test/e2e/run_e2e.sh` | Modify | +100 | Enhanced with parallel, logs, timeout |\n| `test/e2e/kind-config.yaml` | Modify | +30 | Added Redis, multi-node, ports |\n| `Makefile` | Modify | +30 | E2E targets (e2e, e2e-parallel, etc.) |\n| `go.mod` | Modify | +10 | Added e2e-framework, kind, helm, docker, redis |\n| `sdk-python/pyproject.toml` | Modify | +5 | pytest e2e marker configuration |\n| `test/e2e/setup_python_env.sh` | Create | ~20 | Python venv setup script |\n\n**Total: 33 files (27 new, 6 modified), ~1,700+ new test lines**\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### E2E Test Environment Requirements\n\n```bash\n# Prerequisites\n- Kind cluster running (kubectl cluster-info)\n- Docker images built (workloadmanager, router, picod)\n- Helm charts available in manifests/\n- Redis deployed in Kind cluster\n- Python 3.8+ with pytest installed\n```\n\n### Test Execution Strategy\n\n1. **Isolation**: Each test creates unique namespace/testID\n2. **Cleanup**: All tests register cleanup hooks in TestContext\n3. **Parallel**: Tests can run concurrently in separate namespaces\n4. **Timeout**: Each test has explicit timeout (30s-120s)\n5. **Retry**: Flaky operations use retry with backoff\n\n### Test Data Management\n\n- **Fixtures**: YAML CRD templates in fixtures/ directory\n- **Test Scripts**: Python scripts for execution tests\n- **Large Files**: Generated on-demand or pre-created fixtures\n- **Cleanup**: Automatic cleanup via fixture_manager\n\n### Kind Cluster Setup\n\n```bash\n# Create Kind cluster with custom config\nkind create cluster --config test/e2e/kind-config.yaml --name agentcube-e2e\n\n# Load Docker images\nkind load docker-image workloadmanager:latest --name agentcube-e2e\nkind load docker-image router:latest --name agentcube-e2e\nkind load docker-image picod:latest --name agentcube-e2e\n\n# Deploy Helm charts\nhelm install agentcube manifests/charts/agentcube/ --namespace agentcube\n```\n\n### Python SDK E2E Test Pattern\n\n```go\n// Go test calls Python pytest via subprocess\nfunc TestSDKCodeInterpreterE2E(t *testing.T) {\n    cmd := exec.CommandContext(ctx, \"pytest\", \"-v\", \"-m\", \"e2e\", \n        \"test/e2e/python_tests/test_e2e_code_interpreter.py\")\n    cmd.Env = append(os.Environ(),\n        \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://localhost:8080\",\n        \"ROUTER_URL=http://localhost:8081\",\n    )\n    output, err := cmd.CombinedOutput()\n    require.NoError(t, err, \"pytest output: %s\", output)\n}\n```\n\n### Test Coverage Targets\n\n| Component | E2E Test Coverage | Duration |\n|-----------|-------------------|----------|\n| WorkloadManager | 6 tests | ~2 min |\n| Router | 6 tests | ~3 min |\n| PicoD | 6 tests | ~2 min |\n| Session Store | 4 tests | ~1 min |\n| Idle Cleanup | 3 tests | ~16 min (wait for idle) |\n| Warm Pool | 3 tests | ~5 min |\n| CRD Lifecycle | 4 tests | ~3 min |\n| client-go | 4 tests | ~2 min |\n| Python SDK | 11 tests | ~4 min |\n| Integration | 4 tests | ~5 min |\n| **Total** | **47 tests** | **~40 min** |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Framework Setup | T1.1-T1.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Test Fixtures | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: E2E Entry | T3.1-T3.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: WorkloadManager | T4.1-T4.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Router | T5.1-T5.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: PicoD | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Session Store | T7.1-T7.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Idle Cleanup | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 9: Warm Pool | T9.1-T9.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 10: CRD Lifecycle | T10.1-T10.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 11: client-go | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 12: Python Setup | T12.1-T12.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 13: Python CodeInterpreter | T13.1-T13.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 14: Python AgentRuntime | T14.1-T14.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 15: E2E Script | T15.1-T15.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 16: Kind Config | T16.1-T16.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 17: Makefile | T17.1-T17.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 18: Go Modules | T18.1-T18.6 | Pending | 0